---
layout: blog.liquid
title: Collectives | Dhruvang Gajjar
description: Dhruvang, a software engineer with 6+ YoE in web development industry. Product Management, Problem solving and requiement understanding expert.
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
pagination:
    data: collections.collectives
    size: 8
    alias: datas
    reverse: true
---
<div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4">
    {% for post in datas %}
    <a class="xl:w-1/3 md:w-1/2 p-4" href="{{post.url}}">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 h-full shadow-xl">
            <img class="w-full object-cover object-center mb-6"
                src="{{ '/assets/img/' | append: post.data.featuredImg.url | url }}" alt="content">

            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="tracking-widest text-indigo-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">{{post.data.tags[1]}}</h3>
                <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
</div>